description:
This dataset contains the number of New York State live births stratified by county of residence and gestation in weeks. The data presented here may not be the same as the Vital Statistics tables on the DOH public web due to data updates. For more information, check out: 
: http://www.health.ny.gov/statistics/vital_statistics/ or go to the "About" tab.
